Well, you sort of helped, but not really. I want to know how my breakdown is different from what the spoiler says. My steps 4-7 are as follows (With Quotes from the spoiler)<br>
<br>
<br>
#4 - Buy a Ro's Breath Potion, give it Camin to be stripped, get a potion back<br>
<br>
&quot;You can buy Ro's Breath from any of these vendors but you cannot return it to them. Neither of them will turn into Arantir. However, it is confirmed that you can buy Ro's Breath them, take it to Camin to be stripped of it's charge&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
#5 - Give the stripped Potion to Dargon in Halas, this makes Arantir spawn, and potion is returned<br>
<br>
&quot;and then take it to Dargon.&quot; Handing this potion to Dargon in Halas will make her turn into Arantir and the quest will continue.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
#6 - Give the potion to Camin, get a TS faction hit, potion is returned<br>
<br>
&quot;Now take this potion back to Camin in Erudin and hand it to him. He will reply with the following:<br>
<br>
Camin says 'Very interesting... I've seen this work before. Yes, yes! It's the work of Arantir Karondor! Give this back to the person you got it from. Maybe he will have a clue to Arantir's location.' <br>
<br>
Your faction standing with Truespirit got better<br>
You gain experience!!&quot;<br>
<br>
Camin gives you back the potion (it has now been stripped of it's Shield of Lava charge)&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
***#7 - Give the potion to Dargon in Halas (wtf, the spoiler already said Arantir would be spawned in Step #5 - why would Dargon be there again? who do you give this potion to?) Arantir spawns (again?) - Get a note from Arantir.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;and you must take it back to Dargon in Halas.<br>
Note: you cannot skip the previous trip to Camin. You absolutely, must hand the potion to Camin. If you try to skip the trip to Erudin, you will get the following message from Dargon: &quot;I didnt request this item, but thank you very much&quot;.Back in Halas, hand the Ro's Breath potion back to Dargon.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
How is my steps 4-7 different from what the spoiler says?<br>
